%N A317487 Number of 4-cycles in the n-Bruhat graph.
%H A317487 Andrew Howroyd, <a href="/A317487/b317487.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..200</a>
%H A317487 Jennifer Elder, Pamela E. Harris, Jan Kretschmann, and J. Carlos Martínez Mori, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2306.14734">Boolean intervals in the weak order of S_n</a>, arXiv:2306.14734 [math.CO], 2023-2024.
